com.javax0.jdsl.analyzers

Class SimpleAnalysisResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.javax0.jdsl.analyzers.SimpleAnalysisResult
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AnalysisResult

    public class SimpleAnalysisResult
extends Object
implements AnalysisResult
    A simple implementation of the interface AnalysisResult that stores the fields initialized in the constructor values passed as argument and returns them.

    Use the static methods failed(Class)/failed(Class, String) and success(Class, SourceCode, Executor)/ success(Class, SourceCode, Executor, State) to get an instance of the class.

    Author:
    Peter Verhas
